_sText:
**PLEASE NOTE!** 
This is a beta release so it may or may not be stable. If you find any bugs and/or have suggestions please let me know.

**Changes in b1:**
- **Textures**, textured the map with some temporary textures.
- **Lightning**, added lightning to the map.

**Features:**
- **2 areas**, the main area and a "back-room" area with bulletproof one-way glass. To get to the "back-room" area you have to push one of the buttons on the middle pillar (it's the opposite of the side you want to open).
- **Quick action**

**Creator:**
- oskar3123

**Version:**
- b1

**Installation:**
- **1.** Go to your common SteamApps dir. (usually: "C:\Program Files\Steam\SteamApps\common" on 32-bit and "C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\SteamApps\common")
- **2.** Go to your Counter Strike Source dir. (If it's not inside there it's probably in your personal SteamApps dir "C:\Program Files\Steam\SteamApps\<your_username>")
- **3.** Drag the "cstrike" folder there.
